- As a User I can log in
- I can create talk and become a speaker 
    I will get notification after N (N=5) people subscribed to my talk

- I can see all talks 
Speaker can add and remove speakers except himself
I can subscribe for a talk
I can unsubscribe for a talk
I can't subscribe to my own talk

I can specify talk time and place. subscribers will get notifications (immediately, before 2 hours, before 5 mins).

I can create request for a talk, I can suggest speaker, and he'll receive a notification


